      "message": "This is pretty obscure. If someone adds files to the repo and the Build tasks don\u0027t see the new files, this list is not the first thing I would think to check. Not sure how often it will come up.\n\nHow hard would it be to add a presubmit check that every file/dir either has to be listed here or listed as \"not needed for compiles\"?\n\nBTW, if we could just exclude DEPS, go.mod, and go.sum, that would probably cover ~70% of all builds that we can deduplicate. (I can show you the spreadsheet I made if you\u0027re interested.)",
